EXT. PARK - SUNRISE
A man, MAN, is sitting on a bench. A notepad lies on his lap. He is staring at the sunrise, lost in thought. He takes a deep breath and picks up his pen, ready to write.

MAN (v.o.)
Chère Maman... Tu nous manques.

MAN shakes his head and scratches out the words on the notepad. He takes another breath and starts writing again.

MAN (v.o.)
Chère Maman... Je pense au progrès...